   <description> Change permissions on an object for a given group.</description>
   
   
   <discussion><![CDATA[
The A5_CHANGE_PERMISSION() function changes a user password and associated object permissions.
Limitations: Desktop applications only.
   ]]></discussion>
  
   <sections>
   
       <section>
       <title>Example</title>
            <description>The following example is the equivalent of going to "Set Security" for the Customer Information form, and granting access to the admin group.
</description>
            <example><![CDATA[
a5_change_permission("Admin", "customer information at customer.ddd", "form", "run", "grant", "alpha")

]]></example>
       </section>
